"Shhh, I'm here, it's alright."  Despite being a fair bit smaller 
than Starstorm, Phoenix picks her friend up without much difficulty.  
She'd had a lot of practice lugging heavy things around in her days 
as a slave to the Rogues.  "You'll be all right."
